#: ../../S/sport-death.rst:9
msgid ""
"[MIT] The masochistic extreme of hacking, where the body and mind are pushed"
" until their limits are reached, and the body is barely able to support the "
"mind. Then, once your extremes are reached, you push as far beyond that "
"point as you can, far beyond normal notions of all-nighters and caffeine "
"diets."
msgstr ""
"[MIT] "
"ハッキングのマゾヒスティックな極み。心身がその限界に達するまで、そして体がかろうじて心を支えられるまで追い込まれる。それから、いったん極限に達すると、できる限りその地点を越えて、徹夜やカフェイン漬けの通常の概念をはるかに越えて、押し進めるのだ。"
